{
  "stem": "3952.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the yelling and screaming is exactly like you saw on the if you saw the and they come and hit with the stick everything that is making noise to make-- to make-- to put the fear of God into you.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's exactly how it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They drove us out of the house, and they didn't give us too much time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Everything was rush, rush, rush.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we were aware, but we didn't believe it, because we went out to the train station, and we saw people being transported.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know where they were going through.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Czechoslovaks were running away, and they came through Sighet, through the train station of Sighet.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know where that train took them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I haven't got an idea, but we saw them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We saw people evacuating.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We saw people evacuated and running from the Germans, and we-- we knew by the newspapers and by radio.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We new the-- the news, what's going on in Poland, what's going on in the world, in France, when they-- when they got into France.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We knew everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The-- the news reached us like they reached everybody else in the world.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But physically seeing them-- we saw Italian troops passing through Sighet when the Italians were still working together with the-- with the Germans, when they were still fighting.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Later I met Italians when they were prisoners.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They took their weaponry away, and they made them prisoners.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we built houses.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we built-- I was working with a firm that built their heating conditions, you know, their eating-- heating facilities so that the houses be heated, because it was very cold-- but they were prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "They had more rights than we had.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They didn't work as hard.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
